  "tosSection1Title": "Acceptance of Ketentuan",
  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these Ketentuan of Service (\"TerKetentuan If you do not agree to these TKetentuan you must not access or use the Service.",
  "tosSection1Para2": "The Service is provided by {producer} (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\"). These Ketentuan form a legally binding agreement between you and us.",
  "tosSection2Title": "Eligibility & Account",
  "tosSection2Para1": "You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service. If you are under 18, you represent that your parent or legal guardian has read and agreed to these Ketentuan on your behalf.",
  "tosSection2Para2": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for Semua activities that occur under your account. Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.",
  "tosSection3Title": "Kesehatan Information — Not Medical Advice",
  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a Kesehatan companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI Triage feature provides general guidance based on the Gejala you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical eDarurat call your local Darurat number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for Darurat response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "Use of the Service",
  "tosSection4Intro": "You agree NOT to:",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "Use the Service for any unlawful purpose;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble the app;",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Upload content that is malicious, fraudulent, or violates intellectual property rights;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Lainnya users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service to send unsolicited communications or spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Subscriptions & Payments",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EPerusahaan plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tKetentuan",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Batal your subscription at any Waktu through your platform's account sPengaturan",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will not apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Your Data",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Kesehatan data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Privasi Policy, which is incorporated into these Ketentuan by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Ekspor your data at any Waktu via the in-app Ekspor feature, and you may permanently Hapus your account and Semua associated data via Pengaturan → Hapus Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "Disclaimers",
  "tosSection7Para1": "THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\" AND \"AS AVAILABLE\" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, OR NON-INFRINGEMENT.",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI Triage recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "Limitation of Liability",
  "tosSection8Para1": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN Tidak EVENT SHALL {producer} BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO USE) THE SERVICE, WHETHER BASED ON WARRANTY, CONTRACT, TORT, OR ANY Lainnya LEGAL THEORY.",
  "tosSection9Title": "Termination",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and Hapus your account at any Waktu via SPengaturan We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these Ketentuan or if we reasonably believe we are Wajib to do so by law.",
  "tosSection9Para2": "Upon termination, Semua licenses granted to you will end, and your data will be deleted in accordance with our Privasi Policy.",
  "tosSection10Title": "Changes to These Ketentuan",
  "tosSection10Para1": "We may update these Ketentuan from Waktu to tWaktu We will notify you of material changes via the app or by eEmail Continued use of the Service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised TKetentuan",
