  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Privasi Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your Privasi is paramount. This Privasi Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: NNama Email address, Telepon number, Tanggal of birth, and gender. • Kesehatan Data: Blood type, aAlergi chronic conditions, mObat vital signs, symptom logs, and Triage results. • Darurat Contacts: Names, Telepon numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sDukungan • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our Kesehatan companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• Kode QR Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tWaktu • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sPengaturan • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can Ekspor your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: Semua third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View Semua your personal and Kesehatan data within the app or request a data eEkspor • Correction: Edit your Profil information at any Waktu through Edit PProfil • Deletion: Request account deletion through Pengaturan > Data & Privasi > Hapus Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any Waktu without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app Dukungan feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Contact Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns Tentang this Privasi Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • EEmail privacy@vitalseker.com • SDukungan support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to Semua privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
